data.description: New price! Seller to offer $5000 towards buyer closing cost with full price offer! Nestled just minutes from downtown Springfield, in the heart of Marcola, stands this extensively updated home ready to offer its new owners not just a residence, but a testament to great savings and long-lasting value. Outside, the investment in a brand new roof, energy-efficient double pane windows, a new fence with a gate, and a new deck ensures durability and contributes to substantial energy savings over time. The addition of a tool shed and outdoor garden area speaks to sustainable living, providing resources for the long term.Sitting on just under 1/4 acre, this property offers not only space for kiddos and outdoor activities but also an investment in a lifestyle that emphasizes efficiency and lasting value. Inside, the story of savings continues with new flooring throughout, an updated bathroom, and new appliances. The ductless heat pump and wood stove not only enhance comfort but also contribute to energy efficiency, making this home a wise choice for ongoing savings. The sunroom adds a touch of luxury, extending your living space and enhancing the overall value of the property. This home is more than just a purchase; it's a commitment to a future of enduring quality and financial prudence.
